# .railpackignore
#
# This file intentionally overrides .gitignore for Railpack builds.
# dist/ is excluded from version control via .gitignore, but must be
# present in the runtime image so that `node dist/index.js` can start.
# Leaving this file empty (comments only) ensures Railpack includes
# the compiled TypeScript output without inheriting the .gitignore exclusions.
